en topological\nflat band opens a promising route to engineer novel emergent phases of matter\nat the crossroad between strong correlation physics and electronic topology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Feb 2020 18:28:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-12"}
