r to those of Alon, Frankl, and Lov\\'asz \\cite{AFL} and compute the\nconnectivity of certain simplicial complexes that might be of interest in their\nown right.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Feb 2020 12:19:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Feb 2020 13:35:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 22:38:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-09"}
