\nstatistics and also the placement of basin scale eddies. Increasing\nhydrographic coverage further improved the results of IAPexp compared to IAexp\nin the subsurface layers. Switching off multiplicative inflation in IAexp and\nIAPexp leads to further improvements, especially in the subsurface layers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Feb 2020 15:14:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-06"}
